    <item>
      <title>托克集团前首席运营官的律师称，他可能存在疏忽但并非犯罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/ex-trafigura-coo-perhaps-negligent-but-not-criminal-says-lawyer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[托克集团前首席运营官迈克·温赖特的律师向瑞士法庭表示，温赖特可能存在疏忽，但他并不知道自己批准的付款是贿赂，据称是为了获得利润丰厚的安哥拉石油和航运合同。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/ex-trafigura-coo-perhaps-negligent-but-not-criminal-says-lawyer</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 12:28:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国转向巴西 特朗普贸易战将对美国农民造成更大伤害</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/trump-trade-war-to-hurt-us-farmers-more-as-china-turns-to-brazil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普发起的第一次贸易战给美国大豆种植户造成了 110 亿美元的损失。后续影响必定会更严重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/trump-trade-war-to-hurt-us-farmers-more-as-china-turns-to-brazil</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰采取措施阻止主要电视网络的非法收购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/poland-to-protect-private-tv-stations-from-unwanted-takeovers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总理唐纳德·塔斯克誓言要阻止两家私人电视台被不受欢迎的收购者收购，并承诺保护这个欧盟国家的媒体免受外界干涉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/poland-to-protect-private-tv-stations-from-unwanted-takeovers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 11:50:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯可能实施更严厉制裁 油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/latest-oil-market-news-and-analytics-for-dec-11</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于俄罗斯可能加大对原油的制裁，油价上涨，但政府报告显示美国汽油和馏分油库存增加后，油价缩减涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/latest-oil-market-news-and-analytics-for-dec-11</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 23:30:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
